((Update!))

Hey all! Apologies for leaving, things have gotten busy and have been hard to keep up with, especially after the loss of the game…

I’m not 100% sure if I will, but, I may return! I’ve been drawing some oc’s and just kinda, playing around, uhm, here’s some sketches of them!!

The first two you all know~ But the third is a major character who’d be revealed quite soon, if I can get everything remade! But yea! Have a great day!
